<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV46">
<l>tōṭupeṟṟa taṇṭuḻāya laṅkalāṭu ceṉṉiyāy</l>
<l>kōṭupaṟṟi yāḻiyēnti yañciṟaip puḷḷūrtiyāl</l>
<l>nāṭupeṟṟa naṉmainaṇṇa millaiyēṉu nāyiṉēṉ</l>
<l>vīṭupeṟṟi ṟappoṭumpi ṟappaṟukku mācolē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with a head on which play garlands of cool, flowering tulasi!</l>
<l>Holding a horn and carrying a discus, You ride a winged bird!</l>
<l>Even if [I] do not have [even] a trifle of the goodness that the [people of]</l>
<l rend="indent">the land have,</l>
<l>do tell how I, a dog, will sever [the cycle of] births along with deaths,</l>
<l rend="indent">obtaining liberation!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
